projects.name: Cross Platform Excel Clone
projects.description: Created a cross-platform Spreadsheet application using electron that could run on Linux, Mac and windows. Used Jquery, HTML and CSS for UI and adding functionalities to our app. Used Graph and Stack Data Structure to implement excel Formula.

projects.name: PixyWorld
projects.description: An image exploration Web Application created using ReactJS that allows the user to view several random images and find images of the choice.

projects.name: TechniQ
projects.description: A ToDo Web App called TechniQ that helps the user to maintain their task and list everything they have to do. It is helpful in planning the daily schedules efficiently. It gives the user options to Create new task, View all tasks and delete any task.

projects.name: Flexix
projects.description: Created an OTT streaming platform where the user can browse through various movies and webseries using javaScript and reactJs. It is a similar version of netix with my own design touch, showing SignIn page, SignUp Page, browse page and a lot more. This uses Firebase Services for user authentication and Cloud Firestore to sync and store the videos.
